      "options": {
        "content": "## Infrastructure Status — Mac Mini .145\n**Arr Stack** · Sonarr :8989 · Radarr :7878 · Prowlarr :9696 · Sportarr :1867  \n**AI** · LiteLLM :4000 · Open WebUI :3002 · Obot :8090  \n**Core** · Vault :8200 · Home Assistant :8123 · Homarr :7575  \n**QNAP .201** · Plex :32400  \n**Monitoring** · [Uptime Kuma](http://mac-mini.internal:3033) · [Grafana](http://mac-mini.internal:3030)",
        "mode": "markdown"
